Users
    without auth
        view all (Blog index)
        show (Blog show)
    with auth
        comment (add to comments table)
        like (increment Blog likes)

    Writer studio (auth)
        view all
        store
        show
        update
        delete

Comment
    comment on blog (store)
    edit comment (update)
    delete your comment  (delete)


